{"tid":1901375,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[無理解僱] 代通知金疑問","createTime":"2020-02-27T19:52:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T12:53:00.000Z","uid":44804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ef905641376307945c8b270a5dce9c7207d9c577","tid":1901375,"uid":44804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T19:52:17.000Z","msg":"今日收工俾人口頭無理解僱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可惜佢俾d理由都好牽強<br />\n<br />\n個老闆原本話可以留多7日/1個月<br />\n但後尾反口話無得留<br />\n最後問佢拎左今個月人工<br />\n但唔記得問佢拎代通知金<br />\n<br />\n之前見工無簽過約 <br />\n但有roster作紀錄<br />\n<br />\n上極網都唔係好睇唔明<br />\n同埋唔知算唔算係<br />\n請問part time 應該點計同點拎法(不歡而散)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c22cf126558f14a11ec2985fdc5657d5c94022a","tid":1901375,"uid":18741,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T20:00:14.000Z","msg":"Part time邊有代通知金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n返左幾多個鐘或日工咪出幾多人工俾你囉"},{"pid":"bce57e5c3a5d86dd79a692af52fa8fc294361892","tid":1901375,"uid":68430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T20:19:50.000Z","msg":"加油la 遊行+肺炎 好傷經濟"},{"pid":"b7aaf1c841572ac5d36859460d00002a6ade60f0","tid":1901375,"uid":44804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1c22cf126558f14a11ec2985fdc5657d5c94022a","tid":1901375,"uid":18741,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T20:00:14.000Z","msg":"Part time邊有代通知金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n返左幾多個鐘或日工咪出幾多人工俾你囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T20:59:56.000Z","msg":"418喎<br />\n計連續性僱傭合約喎<br />\n你未聽過？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/faq/cap57b_whole.htm#Q2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.labour.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Ffaq%2Fcap57b_whole.htm%23Q2&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0RFNIXSBonesC3SPsSCGYVE%3D&h=aec02e3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/faq/cap57b_whole.htm#Q2</a>"},{"pid":"951726b7a778224701abdd21914929c051be718b","tid":1901375,"uid":57462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T21:22:59.000Z","msg":"過418?<br />\n合約唔一定要有，通知期法例有規定<br />\n你有出過糧已經證明到你受僱（搭單問係咩工？可能對方咬你自僱，不過都有定義）<br />\n代通知金勞工例都寫左點計，勞記見啦"},{"pid":"c1899ec8d9b0eed2be14a372205fbbb3eb7e6f08","tid":1901375,"uid":198234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:53:00.000Z","msg":"同老細講要代通知金先 <br />\npart time通常冇一個月<br />\n<br />\n如果佢唔俾 就上勞工處<br />\n但你要有紀錄證明自己係418"}]}